27
00:01:19,120 --> 00:01:20,280
You'll see results with just three doses.

28
00:01:23,959 --> 00:01:24,359
Wait a moment.

29
00:01:25,799 --> 00:01:26,920
You just mentioned

30
00:01:27,400 --> 00:01:28,799
using the bathroom three to four times a day,

31
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:29,840
all with watery stools,

32
00:01:30,159 --> 00:01:31,120
