45
00:01:48,760 --> 00:01:49,319
Open your mouth.

46
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:00,920
Internal accumulation of dampness-heat.

47
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:01,920
Chronic diarrhea damaging the spleen.

48
00:02:02,319 --> 00:02:03,040
And the pulse is thin and weak.

49
00:02:03,400 --> 00:02:04,239
The pulse is thin and weak.

50
00:02:04,719 --> 00:02:05,799
It's definitely a spleen deficiency.

51
00:02:06,439 --> 00:02:07,760
