86
00:03:21,159 --> 00:03:23,280
I'll find another healer for tomorrow.

87
00:03:27,039 --> 00:03:29,120
This debate isn't about winning or losing.

88
00:03:29,879 --> 00:03:30,439
but to

89
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:32,280
